<item>
            <title>[LU-11696] &quot;lfs getsom&quot; returns &quot;24&quot; (sizeof lustre_som_attr) to userspace</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11696</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs getsom&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; command always returns &quot;24&quot; to userspace because &quot;rc = 24&quot; (sizeof (struct lustre_som_attrs)) after fetching the xattr from the kernel.  If the &lt;tt&gt;lfs_getsom()-&amp;gt;lgetxattr()&lt;/tt&gt; call returns a positive value, then this is the size of the xattr &amp;lt; sizeof(*attrs) and rc should be set to 0 in that case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
